PURPOSE:
  This directory exists to make it easy to aquire a local copy of relevant
  DTDs and other resource files associated with the formats of the
  documentation.

GUIDELINES:
  These are NOT maintained by The Parchive Project and cvs should not be used
  to commit further changes to these files, unless customizations are made for
  the project.

CONTENTS:
  - docbook-simple-1.0

    http://www.oasis-open.org/docbook/xml/simple/1.0/index.shtml

    A copy of the Docbook Simplified DTD, can be used with tools like 'xmllint'
    or 'nsgmls' to that documentation conforms to the standard.  A CSS for
    docbook simplified is also contained within, and can be useful when html
    output is generated.

